im looking through lands here and i want to clarify what i consider utility vs. not:
- fetchlands are color fixing, not utiltiy
- lands with weird CIPT conditions like [[Murmuring Bosk]] are not utility
- Lands with static abilities like Urborg Tomb of Yawgmoth are utility lands
- Obviously things with activated abilities that aren't mana abilities are utility lands
- I think cabal coffers and gaea' cradle are utility land. this is getting tricky...
